message.entry: ''MatchThreshold'' must be less than or equal to ''NumNeighbors''.
words1 and words2 must have the same ''VocabularySize''.
The number of words must equal the number of point locations.
This object only supports one-dimensional indexing.
Expected all objects to be the same class.
